## Dimension: Faithfulness (HARD CONSTRAINT)

**Definition**: The degree to which the narrative accurately represents the synthesis ground truth without introducing novel claims, facilitator interpretations, or distortions.

**Why This Matters**: Scientific advice must be grounded strictly in expert input. Any novel claims, "facilitator gloss", or misinterpretations added during narrative generation undermine trust and compromise the integrity of the Delphi process.

